<br>
I have several mages i have grouped with for a longtime and a few i have guilded with i never thought i would be the person to scream NERF! or want somthin fixed even tho our transport capabilites have been minimalized now with books and transport spires and Graveyards and our spell damge progression has always been gimped as well and lures suck much arse and  are still a thirdrate fix to certain issues.<br>
<br>
Anyways i have always been satisfied with the fact that no matter what our short term dps spell wise was the best in the game and we always topped the other classes by a few levels spell damage wise.  But now i find out that in some kinda misguided attempt to &quot;fix&quot; the mage class outa guilt i guess for gimping their rods P they gave them a 2k dd spell for 61<br>
Lets look at this for a second shall we?<br>
wizards get a 2k damge spell also at 60 but it  drops from some of the toughest mobs in game prePOP and is rare to boot. so i guess they think that by 61 even with the mage debuff abilities and DS and their pets as well by 61 they should be pretty much  balanced with Wizards /yawn yeah right i am not out to nerf the mage class  i really think the solution is to toss a extra 100 or 200 damage on our dds over the 50 to 65 range.<br>
Anyways feel free to toss yer opinions on there biased or non biased so peeps can come draw their own conclusion as to whether they need to spam sony /feedback till they admit they screwed up and fix this. Now i am not knowledgeable enuff on the aa/crits/specialitys to see if they add much of a change to our dps so if you havve more to add concerning that please do <br>
To me it feels like Wizard's are getting the shaft   <p>Heisenberg Uncertainus 44? Wizzie<br>
