<br>
I do have a problem with the efficiency of tallon. Its better then anything I can do untill the much rarer strike of solusek at 65. That to me is a problem. Wizard's need a significant advantage in spell damage over mages so that we don't get completely outdone after you add in mag pets. Since a mag (when bolts are viable) is nuking with a better effeiciency then i am I doubt very much much i am exceeding his damage by much if any.<br>
<br>
My sugesstion:<br>
Change all 60+ draughts to 240 mana which would give them an effeiciency just under firebolt of tallon. Change draught of ro to lvl 61 and put it on a vendor and move tears of ro to 62. Remove lure of thunder from the vendor and add it to the parchment quest thing.<br>
